Class TaskDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.database.sqlite.SQLiteOpenHelper
      • professional.team17.com.professional.Entity.TaskDAO

  • public class TaskDAO
extends android.database.sqlite.SQLiteOpenHelper
    The local db used to ensure the requesters requested tasks match with the server. As well it function to take over in offline state so the user can add/edit tasks in requested state.
